article.description: — Jalen Slawson posted 14 points and five blocks as Furman beat UNC Greensboro 68-49 on Monday.
article.headline: Slawson scores 14 to lift Furman past UNC Greensboro 68-49
article.linkText: Slawson scores 14 to lift Furman past UNC Greensboro 68-49
article.story: GREENVILLE, S.C. -- — Jalen Slawson posted 14 points and five blocks as Furman beat UNC Greensboro 68-49 on Monday. Alex Hunter had 19 points and six rebounds for Furman (12-6, 6-3 Southern Conference). Mike Bothwell added 12 points. Garrett Hien had eight rebounds. Isaiah Miller had 14 points and six steals for the Spartans (13-6, 8-3), whose seven-game winning streak was snapped. Keyshaun Langley added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
